We performed a series of simple manipulations with each approach.

  - Reading the data
  - `print()`
  - `head()`
  - `tail()`
  - Sampling 100 random rows
  - Filtering for "UNK" payment, this is 6434 rows (0.0435% of total).
  - Summarizing the mean fare amount per payment type.

